        <num>71-2707</num>
        <heading>Unlawful possession of hazardous wastes in the second degree</heading>
        <content>
          <p>ยง 71-2707. Unlawful possession of hazardous wastes in the second degree.\n  No person shall:\n  1. Knowingly possess more than one hundred gallons or one thousand\npounds, whichever is less, of an aggregate weight or volume of hazardous\nwastes at a place other than the site of generation; or\n  2. Recklessly possess more than two hundred gallons or two thousand\npounds, whichever is less, of an aggregate weight or volume of hazardous\nwastes at a place other than the site of generation.\n  Unlawful possession of hazardous wastes in the second degree is a\nclass E felony.\n</p>
        </content>
      </section>
